S.FORM: aicu a hip hap (binaljakan: hip hop katua hip hop aya tiamadju) aya tjen mavan a sikudakudan nua seavrika a maqacuvucuvung a kemaizua i amilika. na kemasi kinaizuanan nua seavrika i amilika tiamadju a sisa sikudakudan a seman bulayan, saka ulja papukeljangi tua sepulingelingetj. a tja keljangen uta tua hip hap a kakukakudan nua seavrika i amilika. nu matevelj a caucau a hip hap, liaw a karakudan niamadju a patjelja seman rap, a seman didji (DJ), katua uduli tua breaking. cinalivatan a patagiljan aicu a hip hap, inika tjuruvu a kicapilj. amin a sikataqaljan nua sebronx i niwyuk a lizuk (New York City) i amilika matevetevelj a semenay i kaqepuqepuan niamadju. tazua pakanakuya tiamadju tua kisac katua hulic a sipatavung tua siselapay i rusung sa semansenayi a kiqaung. kaizuan
